Package: moschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Missouri School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Missouri Department of
    Elementary and Secondary Education (DESE). Provides functions for fetching
    enrollment data from the Missouri Comprehensive Data System (MCDS) and
    transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readxl,
    readr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    httr,
    rappdirs
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    scales
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/almartin82/moschooldata
BugReports: https://github.com/almartin82/moschooldata/issues
